{"about_the_game":"section for a game where players need to survive from wildlife, mine resources, craft items and structures,<br />\r\n<br />\r\n Tribes of the Wildlands Resurgence&quot; is an epic open-world survival game that thrusts you into a rugged wilderness teeming with danger and adventure. Your sole objective? Survive at all costs.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this immersive world, you must fend off not only the unforgiving elements of nature but also rival players who are vying for dominance in this untamed land. Hunt or be hunted, it's your choice.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExplore, Gather, Craft:<br />\r\nVenture into the sprawling wilderness and mine trees, rocks, and iron ore to gather essential resources. These resources are the building blocks of your survival, allowing you to craft weapons, tools, and structures. Will you construct a towering fortress to defend against intruders or create hidden shelters to avoid detection?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSurvive the Wild:<br />\r\nThe wilderness is alive with a diverse range of wildlife, each with its own unique behaviors. Be prepared to face off against ferocious predators, or utilize your skills to become a master of the hunt.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nConflict and Strategy:<br />\r\nAs you interact with other players, engage in intense conflicts, negotiate trades, and form uneasy truces. Will you choose to attack rival tribes to plunder their resources or opt for diplomacy in the pursuit of peaceful coexistence?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;Wildlands Resurgence: Tribes of the Wilderness&quot; challenges your survival instincts, strategic prowess, and creativity as you navigate a treacherous world filled with surprises and perils. Will you thrive as a solitary survivor or rise to lead a thriving tribe in the midst of this unforgiving wilderness? The choice is yours. Begin your journey today!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Main level","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2599310/d4b9f